mal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb76fb6fec1f020896c44216ba15fbbc73c6c956","tid":243741,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大聲講 我打燈喇 我望盲點喇 包無死</blockquote><br />\n我師父話唔得<br />\n會當你係癲"},{"pid":"a46f7e36e00648161b6cdc88d4b4fc4c45962906","tid":243741,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"學車冇試過咗大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過以揸車經驗黎講 記得同前車keep得夠距離<br />\n可能要比平時遠 前面有開燈/brake燈就用黎睇距離<br />\n水撥一定要夠快 塊玻璃唔係你話知佢之後抹餐死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊鏡受雨水影響可能好懞 或者隻窗啲水擋住<br />\n記得唔好望死塊鏡 要望下鏡望下前<br />\n落雨聽講鬆手好多 買定P牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076341f056e94ba6b41809a8107c6b78e981f6b8","tid":243741,"uid":15940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>落雨考車大條道理10km爬路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以唔洗入三波？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學雞?<br />\n考牌最少入一次3波<br />\n開得太慢一樣肥<br />\n真係最緊要俾到考官睇你有安全意識<br />\n落唔落雨咪又係咁考"},{"pid":"3aa8cd94041e9633dac8f6ba52b7eac52db321d1","tid":243741,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>落雨考車大條道理10km爬路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以唔洗入三波？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學雞?<br />\n考牌最少入一次3波<br />\n開得太慢一樣肥<br />\n真係最緊要俾到考官睇你有安全意識<br />\n落唔落雨咪又係咁考</blockquote><br />\n30km到啦 3波點都要上一上。<br />\n除非狂塞車咁冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5037a5dd35307b8b3b178f1a490fee528e12c8","tid":243741,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T02:09:43.000Z","msg":"落雨先正，考車根本係愈塞愈好"},